164
00:16:33,710 --> 00:16:36,750
Musím predsa niečo robiť.

165
00:16:36,750 --> 00:16:38,320
Vie o tom celá škola.

166
00:16:45,890 --> 00:16:50,360
Vieš, Yeok-Ho nie je taký zlý.

167
00:16:53,330 --> 00:16:56,830
Síce sa fakt často bil a tak.

168
00:16:58,300 --> 00:16:59,640
Ale aj tak.

169
00:17:02,210 --> 00:17:05,540
<i>Slečna Yang Ah-Yeong z EBS.</i>

170
00:17:05,540 --> 00:17:08,580
<i>Jasné, slečna Dokonalá.</i>

171
00:17:50,020 --> 00:17:51,860
