Číslo 28.

192
00:21:30,980 --> 00:21:32,540
28 tu nie je?

193
00:21:34,510 --> 00:21:36,910
-Áno?
-Prečítaj prvé zadanie.

194
00:21:36,920 --> 00:21:37,920
Dobre.

195
00:21:40,090 --> 00:21:43,620
"It is natural to make mistakes."

196
00:21:45,020 --> 00:21:50,030
"It is terribly wrong to
keep making mistakes."

197
00:21:50,830 --> 00:21:53,530
