214
00:23:31,200 --> 00:23:32,460
Choi Jeong-Woo?

215
00:23:33,770 --> 00:23:35,300
Ty si Choi Jeong-Woo?

216
00:23:37,100 --> 00:23:38,170
Áno.

217
00:23:40,310 --> 00:23:43,910
Ideš sa biť s najlepším bitkárom v Namile.
S Grizlym.

218
00:23:43,910 --> 00:23:45,480
Vie to už každý.

219
00:23:46,650 --> 00:23:50,410
